{"tid":1127342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(本土派) 仇思達share: 而家無咩工可以同「中國」切割, 人都要搵食既","createTime":"2019-04-27T04:59:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T12:07:27.000Z","uid":134071,"like":13,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e2cb157d4ef09465862e8e1f204ba44d851c8ce3","tid":1127342,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T04:59:17.000Z","msg":"之前班人又笑鳩李永達做大陸生意 (但馮檢基同大陸有生意來往, 支持單非, 班人又支持)<br />\n<br />\n黃毓民早前又話台灣不能跟中國大陸完全割斷..... <br />\n<br />\n自喻本土派既人而家都開始叫人放開懷抱 &nbsp;(Myradio節目&quot;天地友政氣&quot;亦以馬來西亞做例子, 指出本土派不應太抗拒偶爾跟極權派合作, 只要行動目標一致就可以) &nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n唉, 難怪而家中共可以漸控制到香港同台灣既民意.....<br />\n<br />\n(張圖來自中移動, 但仇思達話張圖唔係佢cap <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10156871812652254&amp;set=p.10156871812652254&amp;type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D10156871812652254%26set%3Dp.10156871812652254%26type%3D3%26theater&d=wHiIeFeeqtLxwJ75m5qcsxZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=6af0432d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10156871812652254&amp;set=p.10156871812652254&amp;type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/NP1kFON.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNP1kFON.jpg&h=0acf1524&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ccd70c808be4e82a8fba802297b6e0a15dde0ce","tid":1127342,"uid":6604,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:00:51.000Z","msg":"回力鏢又中"},{"pid":"62a6d306f6bb4edd1ae0bd9f791911e03bec0dd4","tid":1127342,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3ccd70c808be4e82a8fba802297b6e0a15dde0ce","tid":1127342,"uid":6604,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:00:51.000Z","msg":"回力鏢又中"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:04:25.000Z","msg":"「搵食啫！犯法呀？」<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iZ1GlXpq_y8\" data